_sText: ************ Bhop_rooster ************ The pictures doesnt show the entire map it is way bigger then that :) Play it and then judge it :P Map by Sv | Razer ( Me) Took 2 days to build and add technical work. Map is extremely hard and insane long. I agree with those who think that dev isnt the prettiest and it lacks detail but i think that a bhop map should be like this and not too detailed. Map has very good fps for old and new pc's reason : dev textures and cheap water and not much unnessecary details. Enjoy it and it is beatable if you spend some time in it :) Enjoy & Have fun!
